21
00:00:45,723 --> 00:00:58,853
[SPEAKER_02]: The purpose of this meeting is to discuss papers 22-508 and 22-538, special permit and class two auto licenses, request by Lyft slash FlexDrive, and paper 22-557, a secondhand articles license request by ProRepair.

22
00:00:59,977 --> 00:01:07,880
