00:17:57,447 --> 00:17:58,508
[SPEAKER_11]: for like a personal vehicle.

263
00:17:58,528 --> 00:18:04,610
[SPEAKER_11]: So you get there in a personal vehicle, rent this because your personal vehicle, maybe it's too old to be a Lyft, right, something like that.

