00:21:27,833 --> 00:21:31,515
[SPEAKER_11]: I don't know if we're moving this out tonight or waiting for traffic study or what, but,

296
00:21:33,037 --> 00:21:36,079
[SPEAKER_11]: If we, when we do move forward, I'd really like to see that condition put on.

297
00:21:36,960 --> 00:21:42,564
