00:24:07,247 --> 00:24:11,308
[SPEAKER_06]: Do you know what the daily rate they're gonna be paying or weekly or monthly rate?

330
00:24:11,408 --> 00:24:18,689
[SPEAKER_06]: And listen, I'm in that same business and I see them there, these people, they work tremendous amount of hours.

331
00:24:19,349 --> 00:24:22,090
[SPEAKER_06]: And I think they work way too many hours to make a,

332
00:24:24,224 --> 00:24:25,825
[SPEAKER_06]: barely a living wage.

333
00:24:27,345 --> 00:24:32,847
[SPEAKER_06]: I understand your model, but I don't like practices of lifting over myself.

334
00:24:33,868 --> 00:24:42,531
[SPEAKER_06]: You're not doing anything illegal, but there should be better compensation and better benefits for these people who really are out there.

335
00:24:43,721 --> 00:24:52,608
[SPEAKER_06]: an awful lot of hours to, I say, to make a lot of, I say, especially with gas being the way it is now, it's gonna, you know, they're gonna be spending more money to rent these vehicles.

336
00:24:52,628 --> 00:24:58,152
[SPEAKER_06]: So that's, you know, like I say, you know, I understand your company, I just don't like how they treat the employees.

337
00:24:59,553 --> 00:25:00,334
[SPEAKER_02]: Thank you, Councilor Carvalho.

338
00:25:00,434 --> 00:25:02,496
[SPEAKER_02]: Any further questions or discussion from the Council?

339
00:25:04,958 --> 00:25:10,182
[SPEAKER_02]: And if I could just essentially just summarize, and this is gonna be a question for Attorney Blake,

340
00:25:10,954 --> 00:25:16,655
[SPEAKER_02]: I think multiple counselors, if not all the counselors have expressed, we are elected to serve in the public interest.

341
00:25:16,695 --> 00:25:25,817
[SPEAKER_02]: And I think a lot of us feel that these types of companies, because of the amount of hours, because of the low pay, because you can get increasingly lower pay depending on how you operate.

342
00:25:26,457 --> 00:25:34,819
[SPEAKER_02]: We have concerns about this operating in our community, but it's my understanding, Attorney Blake, that we are very limited in the reasons for denial.

