00:28:50,462 --> 00:28:53,625
[SPEAKER_07]: from how far away are most drivers coming in?

377
00:28:54,226 --> 00:28:58,850
[SPEAKER_07]: How many hours are they spending on the road and around Medford?

378
00:28:58,870 --> 00:29:10,059
[SPEAKER_07]: I know I've heard from constituent concerns about when the hourly rate for a driver gets low, of course that could incentivize drivers to drive more.

379
00:29:10,099 --> 00:29:16,505
[SPEAKER_07]: We wanna make sure that we are not creating an incentive structure in Medford wherein drivers are

380
00:29:17,180 --> 00:29:24,164
