381
00:29:24,184 --> 00:29:30,868
[SPEAKER_07]: So I'd be curious to entertain if Representative Goodlift could provide that type of information for a future meeting.

382
00:29:31,008 --> 00:29:31,308
[SPEAKER_07]: Thank you.

383
00:29:32,409 --> 00:29:33,209
[SPEAKER_02]: Thank you, Councilor Collins.

384
00:29:33,229 --> 00:29:43,795
[SPEAKER_02]: So I just wanna make sure you're asking to see if a similar metropolitan area could provide information related to daily rates, compensation, where folks are traveling from.

385
00:29:44,683 --> 00:30:02,516
[SPEAKER_07]: That would be if Lyft could provide for, you know, for an example or two of metropolitan areas similar to Medford, average hourly wage, average daily wage, how many hours per day drivers are spending on the roads, how far away they are traveling to Medford to pick up those cars.

386
00:30:07,139 --> 00:30:08,020
[SPEAKER_02]: Thank you, Councilor Collins.

387
00:30:08,620 --> 00:30:13,904
[SPEAKER_02]: Christy, is that something that, is that data that's available that might be able to be provided either now or in the future?

388
00:30:16,627 --> 00:30:19,788
[SPEAKER_01]: I mean, it's not information that we would be sharing.

389
00:30:19,808 --> 00:30:26,851
[SPEAKER_01]: And part of it too is, you know, this is for us asking for permission for the rentals use.

390
00:30:27,151 --> 00:30:38,915
