409
00:32:07,763 --> 00:32:11,584
[SPEAKER_06]: They're not getting when they do the right share service from other people.

410
00:32:12,124 --> 00:32:22,306
[SPEAKER_06]: So again, I know there's not much, I know we don't get to stipulate what you pay your employees or don't pay them.

411
00:32:22,707 --> 00:32:32,529
[SPEAKER_06]: That's not within our purview, but I do think, I don't support your model for what you do with employees.

412
00:32:33,449 --> 00:32:34,369
[SPEAKER_02]: Thank you, Councilor Kerrio.

413
00:32:34,389 --> 00:32:36,970
[SPEAKER_02]: To that point, Christy, if we're using

